    "body": "This is not as straightforward as I thought. Problem is the metrics need to be enabled super early on start: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/335914a63afae019a2b901d88f13b28eb0d6ca58/metrics/metrics.go#L45\r\n\r\nConfig file processing happens much later on. Only way I see is to manually extract the enable flag from the config file in `metrics.init()` which adds on top of the hack.\r\n\r\nI'll put this issue on hold until there's a better idea how to handle it.",
